口述实录 | 住在隔离点外帐篷里的老公，我等你回来过30岁生日！。
Oral record & # 144; & # 45; My husband in the tent outside the quarantine. I'll be back for your 30th birthday!
亚楠、陈冰。
Yanan, Chen Bing.
新民周刊                      。
Xinmin Weekly.
